//data modeling garda relationship is important-----------------------------------------------------------------------
----------Relationship with data:- 1) 1 to 1   2) 1 to few   3) 1 to many   4) 1 to ton   5)many to many
Referenced - normalized -- chuttai banauni parent ma child ko reference matra halni like id.. -- esma diff api bata info aucha (diff queries) 1 to many, 1 to ton, many to many ma referencing
-child referencing -- child lai parent ma attach garni array ma(movie ma actors haru ko id attach)(! to few)
-parent referencing -- child ma chai parent ko id halni (1 to many, 1 to ton)
-two-way referencing -- parent ma pani child ko child ma pani parent ko (many to many ma)

Embedded - denormalized -- eutai ma banauni for rg: movie ko case ma actor haru eutai ma halni actor kei document ma -- eutai api bata sabai info aucha (one query) 1 to few, 1 to many(Depends) ma embedding -- data dherai ccha tara change hudaina bhane pani embed
